.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5604%2F4433310&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=b7e4a617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5604/4433310</a><br />\n<br />\n但真係敢開學喎"},{"pid":"72b64804fb5f40cb28e124d24f3e16e7b0ef13cb","tid":1937061,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦 真條毛咩 仲有好多確診 不過支那唔俾報 就係為左之後個國際話語權 咪撚帶風向屌你老母"}]}